Frequently Asked Questions

Common questions about our pricing and services

Do you offer custom pricing for large projects?

Yes! For enterprise projects or bulk orders, we offer custom pricing based on your specific requirements. Contact us for a personalized quote.

What's included in the support plans?

Our support plans include regular updates, bug fixes, security patches, monitoring, and technical support. Higher tiers include priority support and additional features.

Can I upgrade or downgrade my plan?

Absolutely! You can upgrade or downgrade your support plan at any time. For project-based services, we can discuss modifications during development.

Do you offer payment plans?

Yes, we offer flexible payment plans for larger projects. Typically, we require 50% upfront and 50% upon completion, but we can discuss custom payment schedules for your needs.
